*[[1991]] &amp;ndash; [[Ronald McKie]], Australian author (b. 1909)
*[[1992]] &amp;ndash; [[Wilbur Mills]], American politician (b. 1909)
*[[1995]] &amp;ndash; [[Michael Hordern]], English actor (b. 1911)
*[[1997]] &amp;ndash; [[John Eccles (neurophysiologist)|John Eccles]], Australian neurophysiologist, [[Nobel Prize in Physiology or Medicine|Nobel laureate]] (b. 1903)
*  1997   &amp;ndash; [[Paulo Freire]], Brazilian educator and theorist (b. 1921)
*[[1998]] &amp;ndash; [[hide (musician)|hide]], Japanese singer-songwriter, musician, producer, and actor ([[X Japan]] and [[Zilch (band)|Zilch]]) (b. 1964)
*  1998   &amp;ndash; [[Justin Fashanu]], English footballer (b. 1961)
*  1998   &amp;ndash; [[Kevin Lloyd]], English actor (b. 1949)
*  1998   &amp;ndash; [[Gene Raymond]], American actor (b. 1908)
*[[1999]] &amp;ndash; [[Douglas Harkness]], Canadian politician (b. 1903)
