*[[2001]] &amp;ndash; [[Gina Mastrogiacomo]], American actress (b. 1961)
*  2001   &amp;ndash; [[Ted Rogers (comedian)|Ted Rogers]], English comedian (b. 1935)
*[[2002]] &amp;ndash; [[W. T. Tutte]], English-Canadian codebreaker and mathematician (b. 1917)
*[[2005]] &amp;ndash; [[Kenneth Clark (psychologist)|Kenneth B. Clark]], American psychologist (b. 1914)
*  2005   &amp;ndash; [[Wee Kim Wee]], Singaporean politician, 4th [[President of Singapore]] (b. 1915)
*[[2006]] &amp;ndash; [[Louis Rukeyser]], American columnist (b. 1933)
*[[2007]] &amp;ndash; [[Brad McGann]], New Zealand director and screenwriter (b. 1964)
*[[2008]] &amp;ndash; [[Beverlee McKinsey]], American actress (b. 1940)
*[[2009]] &amp;ndash; [[Kiyoshiro Imawano]], Japanese singer, musician, producer, and actor ([[RC Succession]]) (b. 1951)
